long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A browser extension that allows doctors to write medical encounters faster with GPT.

Doctors waste hours everyday slaving away over their EMR. Not anymore! Doctor Oakwin is the latest and best tool that can help doctors write their medical encounter notes faster than ever before!

All you have to do is download the extension, and when you write, click on us and ask the AI to help out!
